'''[[can]] [[of]] [[worms]]'''

#{{idiom}} An [[issue]] whose [[resolution]] is difficult, [[contentious]], or unusually [complicated].  The problem itself does not have to be complex.  
#:''Stating that a certain individual was the greatest person who ever lived would definitely open a '''can of worms'''.''
#A very [[complex]], or [[unsolvable]] [[problem]].  Once the topic is raised, subsequent or related problems will also need to be addressed.